games.description: Valorant is a free-to-play, team-based action-adventure game developed and published by Riot Games. It was released on November 14, 2017 for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One.
games.name: Valorant

games.description: League of Legends is a free-to-play, team-based, realm-based hack and slash online video game developed and published by Riot Games. It is the first game in the League of Legends series and the successor to the original Lineage series.
games.name: League Of Legend

games.description: Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS: GO) is a first-person shooter video game developed and published by Valve Corporation. It is the successor to Counter-Strike, and the third installment in the Counter-Strike series.
games.name: Counter Strike:Global Offensive

games.description: Dota 2 is a multiplayer online battle arena video game developed by Valve Corporation and released in 2007 as DotA. It is the second major installment in the Warcraft series, following Warcraft III: Reign of Chaos and preceding the expansion pack DotA 2: Full-erton.
games.name: Dota 2

games.description: Assassin's Creed: Valhalla is a 2017 action-adventure video game developed by Ubisoft Quebec and published by Ubisoft. It is the first installment in the Assassin's Creed series and the sequel to the 2010 video game Assassin's Creed.
games.name: Assasin's Creed Valhala

games.description: Hitman: Absolution is a 2018 action-adventure video game developed by Ubisoft Quebec and published by Ubisoft. It is the second installment in the Assassin's Creed series and the sequel to the 2010 video game Assassin's Creed.
games.name: Hitman: Absolution

games.description: cyberpunk 2077 is a 2018 action-adventure video game developed by CD Projekt and published by CD Projekt. It is the first installment in the Cyberpunk series and the sequel to the 2011 video game Cyberpunk.

games.description: GTA V is a 2018 action-adventure video game developed by Rockstar North and published by Rockstar Games. It is the fifth installment in the Grand Theft Auto series and the successor to Grand Theft Auto IV.
